<h2 id="move-shiploader-to-the-container">Move ShipLoader to the Container <a class="headerlink" href="container-wrapup#move-shiploader-to-the-container" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Keep going! We don't want to instantiate a <code>ShipLoader</code> object manually in
<code>battle.php</code> and <code>index.php</code>. Let's just do it inside <code>Container</code>.</p>
<p>Follow the same pattern: create a <code>private</code> property called <code>$shipLoader</code>,
and a <code>public function getShipLoader()</code>:</p>
